dct_title_s: Automobile road from Los Angeles, Cal. to Phoenix, Ariz. San Bernardino - Brawley - Yuma - Phoenix
dct_description_sm: Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
Oriented with north toward upper left.
Shows roads, railroads, city plans, waterways.
Indicates distances from Los Angeles and Phoenix.
Numbered 187 in lower right, 4 in upper right, and 63 in left margin.
Belongs to a series of strip maps showing roads in California.
